  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-05 adversarial sample)",
  "description": "Synthetic V&V 40 credibility package for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under VAD conditions. COU2 requires prediction of absolute hemolysis index values across pulsatile operating envelopes at MRL 5. The validation result presented here references a steady-state benchtop comparator dataset; the COU explicitly requires pulsatile flow assessment. This package embeds W-AR-05 (comparator absence or mismatch) via D3 undercutting: the inference from the steady-state comparator to pulsatile-COU credibility is methodologically unsound. One validation result intentionally omits the comparedAgainst link to expose the SHACL detection surface.",
